definition: nature/character/property/quality/attribute/sexuality/sex/gender/suffix forming adjective from verb/suffix forming noun from adjective, corresponding to -ness or -ity/essence/CL:個|个[ge4]

sentences.english: Make your records available to the local and national record committees.
sentences.chinese: 將自己的紀錄提供給地區或是全國性的紀錄委員會。

sentences.english: Our club has affiliated with a national society.
sentences.chinese: 我們俱樂部已與一個全國性協會合並。

sentences.english: It was too late to prevent the story from appearing in the national newspapers.
sentences.chinese: 要阻止全國性報紙刊登這件事已經爲時過晚。

sentences.english: He is counted as a national hero.
sentences.chinese: 那個國家發起了一場全國性的反貪污運動。

sentences.english: The boomerang kid phenomenon has become a social problem on a nationwide scale.
sentences.chinese: 啃老族已成爲全國性的社會問題。

sentences.english: Chapters of Medical Students for Choice fundraise in order for members to attend the national conference.
sentences.chinese: 自由醫學社團籌款旨在爲讓成員們參加全國性的會議。

sentences.english: The teachers tried to whomp up students' interest in a national student strike.
sentences.chinese: 老師們試圖激起學生舉行一次全國性罷課。

sentences.english: Safeco relies on a large national network of independent agents and brokers to help customers identify their best possible coverage.
sentences.chinese: Safeco建設了一個全國性的代理商網絡。

sentences.english: A national electronic-money system would operate as a debit-card system.
sentences.chinese: 一個全國性的電子貨幣系統如同結算卡系統那樣運行。

sentences.english: The researchers obtained data from a national pizza delivery company.
sentences.chinese: 研究人員從一家全國性的披薩外送公司獲取數據。

sentences.english: It will also set up a national cap and trade system.
sentences.chinese: 該議案還將建立一個全國性限額和交易機制。

sentences.english: The competition can be fierce, and it foreshadows a larger national event.
sentences.chinese: 競爭可能非常激烈，是爲大型的全國性比賽熱身的。

sentences.english: A nationwide manhunt for an alleged child molester is over.
sentences.chinese: 一次對所謂未成年人性騷擾的全國性搜捕運動結束了。

sentences.english: The concert was to kick off a nationwide voter registration drive.
sentences.chinese: 這場音樂會旨在開始全國性的選民登記運動。

sentences.english: A phony DJ trapped in a national playlist?
sentences.chinese: 被限制在全國性播放歌單裏的假模假式的DJ？

sentences.english: The national single event structure is perpendicular and of many gradations.
sentences.chinese: 全國性單項競賽組織機構呈垂直多層次化結構。
